{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember much more than the fact that, you know, it was scary and, and I don't think I got a very good understanding of, of what the difference was between me and my friends at that point.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think there was any talk about it until when, when we were gone, and then our friends were explained by their, their parents what had happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then spent another day in our, in our own house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the following day, now we up to the 28th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tell you, the 29th I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The 28th, again, we, we slept at our friend's house, but again went back to school the following day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The 29th was the king's birthday, and my father's birthday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And usually there was-- we would go in and celebrate the king at the castle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But because of the situation in the country, there was no celebration for the king.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and I believe that was the night of Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now I get a little muddled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think that-- yeah, this-- yeah, this, the 29th, again, we did not sleep at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the 30th, we left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We left Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was the, I believe that was the night of Rosh Hashanah, where, where the Jewish community was being warned, and the rabbi in temple told everybody that there would be no service, that they should all leave and tell everybody they, they could tell to also leave.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and that there would be an action very shortly after that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed with neighbors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived, we lived on a, on a main road, but behind us was a small, private road with, with houses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these houses were all friends who lived in them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
